defaultInterest Statement
default: Professor Pidgeon currently serves as a member of the Chief Scientist’s Science Advisory Group (SAG) at the Department of Energy and Climate Change, and vice-Chair of the DEFRA/DECC Social Sciences Expert Panel (SSEP). 
defaultDr Adam Corner, in addition to his role at Cardiff University, also works for the Climate Outreach &amp; Information Network charity (www.climateoutreach.org.uk). 
defaultThe opinions here are, however, offered solely in relation to the authors’ professional academic positions at Cardiff.
